parts.text:
Magpie

```json
{
  "application": "Magpie",
  "description": "Magpie is a framework that enables running Hadoop-based applications on traditional HPC systems like SLURM.",
  "job_type": "tensorflow-horovod",
  "tensorflow_horovod_job": "synthetic-benchmark",
  "dependency": "mpirun",
  "resource_requirements": {
    "slurm": {
      "nodes": "<my_node_count>",
      "time": "<my_time_in_minutes>",
      "job_name": "<my_job_name>",
      "partition": "<my_partition>"
    },
    "magpie": {
      "scripts_home": "${HOME}/magpie",
      "local_dir": "/tmp/${USER}/magpie",
      "python": "/usr/bin/python3"
    },
    "tensorflow_horovod": {
      "setup": "yes",
      "local_dir": "/tmp/${USER}/tensorflow-horovod"
    }
  },
  "scripts": [
    "magpie-check-inputs",
    "magpie-setup-core",
    "magpie-setup-projects",
    "magpie-setup-post",
    "magpie-pre-run",
    "magpie-run-distributed",
    "magpie-cleanup",
    "magpie-post-run"
  ]
}
```
